It would be nice to have the option of assigning different locations for storing attachments on a per-category, or even per-project basis. 

This would provide better hardware management and support, particularly if one category/project clutters up their allocation of disk space with attachments - it would not affect any another categories/projects as they would store attachments in a different location.

